                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirement</strong> An opponent within reach has @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Raise a Shield]{Raised a Shield}.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> Hargulka snatches at a foe's shield, pulling it out of the way. He attempts an @Check[type:athletics|defense:reflex] check against the Reflex DC of an opponent who has Raised a Shield before making a jaws Strike against the opponent. If the Athletics check succeeds, the shield is not considered raised against the jaws Strike. On a critical success, Hargulka pulls the shield out of position, so it is no longer raised until the opponent Raises the Shield again. This counts as two attacks toward Hargulka's multiple attack penalty, but the multiple attack penalty doesn't increase until after the jaws Strike.</p>"
